OL,3,CChancellor says she will 'make sums
OL,4,Cup' over public sector pay rises
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has said the
OL,7,Fgovernment will "make sure the sums
OL,8,Fadd up" if public sector workers are
OL,9,Fgiven above inflation pay rises.
OL,11,FReports which first appeared in The
OL,12,FTimes suggest independent pay review
OL,13,Fbodies have recommended the 5.5% rise
OL,14,Ffor teachers and around 1.3 million
OL,15,FNHS staff.
OL,17,FSpeaking to the BBC, the Chancellor
OL,18,Fsaid she valued public service workers
OL,19,Fand that "people won't have long to
OL,20,Fwait for a decision".
