OL,3,CChancellor says she will 'make sums
OL,4,Cup' over public sector pay rises
OL,6,F"There is a cost to not settling, a
OL,7,Fcost of further industrial action, and
OL,8,Fa cost in terms of the challenge we
OL,9,Fface recruiting," she told Sunday with
OL,10,FLaura Kuenssberg, stressing her
OL,11,Fspending rules were "non-negotiable".
OL,13,F"We will do it in a proper way and
OL,14,Fmake sure the sums add up."
OL,16,FShe also said the government would
OL,17,Fcarry out a review of pensions to help
OL,18,Fstimulate growth by unlocking cash in
OL,19,Fschemes.
