OL,3,CChancellor says she will 'make sums
OL,4,Cup' over public sector pay rises
OL,6,F"People who make sacrifices and save
OL,7,Fevery month to put something aside for
OL,8,Ftheir retirement, they deserve better
OL,9,Fthan the returns they're getting on
OL,10,Fthose savings today," she said, adding
OL,11,Fthere was an "urgency" from the
OL,12,Fgovernment to unlock investment.
OL,14,FPaul Johnson, director of the
OL,15,Finfluential Institute for Fiscal
OL,16,FStudies, said the public sector would
OL,17,Fbe in pay rises across the economy,
OL,18,Fand would cost an extra #3 billion for
OL,19,Fschools and the NHS alone.
