OL,3,CChancellor says she will 'make sums
OL,4,Cup' over public sector pay rises
OL,6,FHe told the BBC: "In terms of the
OL,7,Fcost, there isn't a specific number
OL,8,Fthat is budgeted for schools, it's
OL,9,Fprobably 1 or 2%, it's certainly
OL,10,Fnothing like 5.5%, so we'd certainly
OL,11,Fbe looking at at least an additional
OL,12,F#1 billion on schools' costs relative
OL,13,Fto what they're currently expecting.
OL,15,F"And a number at least double that
OL,16,Facross the NHS if the proposals for
OL,17,Fthe NHS are similar, which it appears
OL,18,Fthat they might be."
